      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically robust, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been proactively serviced, ensuring the 8,400 RPM redline remains a reliable reality. The chassis remains taut with M-specific suspension geometry and a functional M-Variable Differential Lock providing exceptional lateral grip. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with enthusiast use, the performance envelope is fully intact. Recent fluid analysis confirms healthy internals, and the factory carbon-fiber roof helps maintain a low center of gravity. A visceral, high-revving machine optimized for technical driving.",
